item.title: CVE-2023-42463|2024-10-24T15:29:24.764Z -- wazuh -- wazuh
item.description: Wazuh is a free and open source platform used for threat prevention, detection, and response. This bug introduced a stack overflow hazard that could allow a local privilege escalation. This vulnerability was patched in version 4.5.3.
